  "title": "numericSelector throws an error with routing",
  "body": "**Describe the bug 🐛**\r\n\r\nThe method `getWidgetSearchParameters` of the connector [`connectNumericSelector`](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/src/connectors/numeric-selector/connectNumericSelector.js#L193-L213) throws an error when one of the provided options don't have a an associated value. We have to handle the case where an option don't have a value.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce 🔍**\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/zq7pm74q43\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\nhttps://discourse.algolia.com/t/numeric-selector-default-value/6378\r\n",
